<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="free-adj">free <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /friː/    美 /friː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>自由的；无约束的；随心所欲的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Men are born free. 
人人生而自由。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You have a <strong>free choice</strong>. 
你可以自由选择。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) free to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should feel free to call or visit me.
你可以随时给我打电话或者来找我。</p><footer>2009 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>空闲的；(房屋等) 空余的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are you free this afternoon? 
你今天下午有空吗？</p><footer>2009 陕西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are there any free rooms in your hostel?
你们旅馆还有空房吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>免费的；免税的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Admission is free. 
免费入场。</p><footer>2008 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The workers there enjoy free medical care.
那儿的工人享受免费医疗。</p></div>

<p>注: free常与名词构成合成词，意为“不含…的”、 “无…的”。如：  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>tax-free goods
免税商品</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fat-free milk
脱脂牛奶</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>carefree
无忧无虑的</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="for-free">for free</h3>
<p>1.<strong>免费：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I worked for free for a non-profit organization.
我曾无偿为一个非营利性组织工作过。</p></div>

<h3 id="free-from">free from</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不受…影响的；没有…的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>(be) free from work / duty 
不工作/不值班</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The most pleasant thing of the rainy season is that one can be entirely free from dust.
雨季最令人愉快的是可以完全没有尘土。</p><footer>2016 北京</footer></div>

<h3 id="free-of">free of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>无…的；摆脱了…的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was several weeks before he was completely free of pain.
过了几星期他的疼痛才完全消除。</p></div>

<h3 id="set-free">set … free</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使获得自由；释放：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bird was set free.
鸟儿重新获得了自由。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Set your imagination free when you think about the future.
展望未来时要尽情想象。</p></div></div>